title: '"We are constantly in touch with the greatest mystery in the universe: The moment of consciousness ... You''re stuck in traffic, in your car. The traffic is not moving. You''re annoyed. This is the most amazing thing in the universe."'
pid: a44a6948-d8c9-462c-b2e7-af19e2767fac
body: |2-
  -- Yuval Noah Harari (on People I Mostly Admire, 22/7/2022
